title: Stainless, Quartz Counters, W/D in Unit- Welcome Home. Ground Floor
map_address: 7901 Delridge Way SW near Holden SW
posting_body: Come home to the peace and comfort of Lighthouse.
This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 688 Sq.
Lighthouse offers spacious townhomes and apartments on 12 acres of beautiful grounds.
Located in the popular Westwood neighborhood, Lighthouse is just minutes from the West Seattle Bridge, with easy access to Downtown Seattle via car or bus.
Our homes feature modern comforts like two-story floor plans, oversized closets and wood burning fireplaces.
Picture yourself falling asleep to the sound of a rushing creek, and waking up to play fetch with Rover at our on-site dog park before you join your neighbors for a BBQ at the pool.
A home at Lighthouse is more than just a place to live - it's a community.
- Washer and Dryer in Each Home
- •VERY Pet Friendly with Off-Leash Dog Park on Site
Monday, Wednesday and Friday 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM
Four-legged creatures need a good home too....and they find one here.
Up to two pets per home are welcome, breed restrictions do apply.
Don't forget about our onsite off leash dog park!
While we know that most pets are upstanding citizens, we do have a pet deposit of $300 per pet and a monthly pet rent charge of $50 per month for dogs, and $35 per month for cats.
Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.
If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.
Please contact our leasing team with any questions.
